10.1 Identity Reconstruction

For people who feel lost or directionless.

10.2 Transition Navigation

Major life changes:
career, relationships, location, identity shifts.

10.3 Veteran Reintegration

Rebuilding identity after high-intensity roles.

10.4 Founders and Creators

Aligning action with mission and narrative arc.

10.5 Therapy Augmentation

Non-clinical narrative clarity to support healing.

10.6 Emotional Regulation

Meaning reframes emotional storms.

